  "prompt": "Which companies work for advertising and promotion of FlipKart?",
  "response": "Flipkart, one of India\u2019s leading e-commerce platforms, works with a variety of companies for advertising and promotion. These typically include advertising agencies, creative agencies, media buying agencies, and digital marketing firms to manage its brand campaigns, media placements, and promotional activities. While the specific agencies working with Flipkart may vary over time, some well-known companies and agencies that have been associated with Flipkart\u2019s marketing efforts include:\n\n### 1. **Advertising and Creative Agencies**\n   - **Ogilvy India**: A leading creative agency that has worked on several campaigns for Flipkart.\n   - **Wunderman Thompson (formerly JWT India)**: Known for handling brand strategy and creative campaigns.\n   - **Leo Burnett**: Another prominent agency involved in creative advertising for Flipkart.\n   - **DDB Mudra**: Has worked on innovative campaigns for the brand.\n\n### 2. **Media Buying and Planning Agencies**\n   - **GroupM**: One of the world\u2019s largest media investment groups, handles media planning and buying for Flipkart.\n   - **Zenith**: Part of the Publicis Groupe, involved in media strategy and execution.\n\n### 3. **Digital Marketing and Social Media Agencies**\n   - **Sokrati**: A digital marketing agency specializing in performance marketing and social media campaigns.\n   - **WATConsult**: Known for its work in social media and digital strategy.\n   - **Reprise**: Focuses on digital media planning and execution.\n\n### 4. **Influencer and Content Marketing**\n   - **Viral Nation**: Specializes in influencer marketing and content creation.\n   - **Qyuki**: Focuses on content creation and storytelling for brands.\n\n### 5. **PR and Communications**\n   - **Edelman India**: A leading PR agency handling Flipkart\u2019s public relations and corporate communications.\n   - **Adfactors PR**: One of India\u2019s largest PR firms, involved in shaping Flipkart\u2019s image.\n\n### 6. **In-House Marketing Team**\n   Flipkart also has a robust in-house marketing team that collaborates with external agencies to create and execute campaigns.\n\nThese partnerships help Flipkart maintain its strong brand presence, especially during major sales events like the **Big Billion Days**. The specific agencies may change based on campaigns, but these are some of the key players in Flipkart\u2019s advertising ecosystem.",
